Bloom Tree Partners, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 12:35 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Bloom Tree Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bloom Tree Partners, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to endowments. The firm also manages separate client focused portfolios. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in value stocks. It employs a long/short equity strategy to make its investments. The firm also employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up approach to create its portfolios. It obtains external research to make its investments. The firm was formerly known as Apos Capital Management, LLC. Bloom Tree Partners, LLC was founded in February 2008 and is based in New York City.


101 Park Avenue33rd FloorNew York, NY 10178United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 212-716-2615

Fax: 917-591-2970








