Alok Agrawal: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 12:35 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Bloom Tree Partners, LLC



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Alok   Agrawal  Founder, CEO, MD, Managing Member, & Portfolio Manager, Bloom Tree Partners, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 0 different industries.See Board Relationships----
Background

		Mr. Alok Agrawal is the Founder, Chief Executive Officer, Managing Director, Managing Member, and Portfolio Manager at Bloom Tree Partners, LLC. Mr. Agrawal serves as a managing Member at Bloom Tree GP, LLC. Prior to this, Mr. Agrawal joined Tiger Management L.L.C. as an Analyst and also served as its Co-Portfolio Manager. While at the firm, he analyzed and invested in companies along a wide range of industries including energy, technology, internet, telecom, building ... materials, industrials, financial services, and metals. Previously, he served as an Associate at Bessemer Venture Partners. Prior to this Mr. Agrawal served as a Product Manager at Oracle where he began his professional career and was responsible for new product development efforts, sales-force training, developer education, collateral development, and oversaw a product management team. At Oracle, he also worked as a Development Manager and as an Engineer. Mr. Agrawal serves as a Member of Advisory Board of Lead Edge Capital Management, LLC. He was awarded the President’s Gold Medal at Indian Institute of Technology, Kanpur. Mr. Agrawal graduated from Harvard Business School in 2002 where he was elected a Siebel Scholar and Baker Scholary where he was elected a Baker Scholar and a Siebel Scholar. He also holds a Masters of Science degree in Computer Science from the University of California and a Bachelor of Technology degree in Computer Science from the Indian Institute of Technology, Kanpur.Read Full Background




